OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FMore than 500 people are feared dead
OL,7,Fafter reports that two boats carrying
OL,8,Fmembers of Myanmar's persecuted
OL,9,FRohingya minority have capsized in the
OL,10,FBay of Bengal, officials said on
OL,11,FThursday.
OL,13,FThe two boats left Myanmar's western
OL,14,Fstate of Rakhine in late June carrying
OL,15,Fmostly Rohingya passengers, including
OL,16,Fsome who had traveled from refugee
OL,17,Fcamps across the border in Bangladesh,
OL,18,Faccording to a statement from the
OL,19,FInternational Organization for
OL,20,FMigration and the United Nations High
OL,21,FCommissioner for Refugees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
