OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784193509
OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FOne boat, believed to have been
OL,7,Fcarrying around 250 people, lost
OL,8,Fcontact shortly after departure. A
OL,9,Fsecond boat, reportedly carrying 280
OL,10,Fpeople, is believed to have sunk off
OL,11,FMyanmar's Ayeyarwady coast on July 8.
OL,13,FWhile the incidents and casualty
OL,14,Ffigures have yet to be officially
OL,15,Fconfirmed, UNHCR and IOM are gravely
OL,16,Fconcerned by the potentially
OL,17,Fdevastating loss of life," the
OL,18,Fagencies said.
OL,26,@yD@ZO]
