OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FThe Rohingya, who have in recent years
OL,7,Ffled both Myanmar and Bangladesh's
OL,8,Fsqualid refugee camps by the
OL,9,Fthousands, typically avoid such boat
OL,10,Fjourneys at this time of year, when
OL,11,Fmonsoons are frequent and conditions
OL,12,Fat sea are particularly dangerous.
OL,14,FThe UNHCR and IOM noted this in their
OL,15,Fstatement, saying that recent
OL,16,Ftorrential rain and flooding across
OL,17,Fthe region would have made such
OL,18,Fjourneys especially risky.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
