OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FAround 1.2 million stateless,
OL,7,Fpredominantly Muslim Rohingya remain
OL,8,Ftrapped in overcrowded refugee camps
OL,9,Fin Bangladesh after fleeing waves of
OL,10,Fviolence by Myanmar's security forces.
OL,12,FThe refugees have no way to safely
OL,13,Freturn to Myanmar, where the military
OL,14,Fthat killed thousands of Rohingya in
OL,15,F2017 during what the United States
OL,16,Fdeclared a genocide remains in charge
OL,17,Fof their homeland. The Rohingya still
OL,18,Fliving in Myanmar face severe
OL,19,Frestrictions and many are confined to
OL,20,Finternment camps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
