OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FSteep cuts to foreign aid by the US
OL,7,Fand other countries have led to ration
OL,8,Fcuts in Bangladesh's refugee camps,
OL,9,Fwhile the ruling military and an
OL,10,Fethnic armed organization in Rakhine
OL,11,Fhave fought for control of the region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
