OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FThe unrest has led to an increasing
OL,7,Fnumber of Rohingya attempting to make
OL,8,Fthe dangerous ocean crossing to
OL,9,FMalaysia on rickety boats. Thousands
OL,10,Fhave died in the process, including
OL,11,Fbabies, children and pregnant women.
OL,12,FLocal maritime authorities have
OL,13,Ffrequently abandoned the Rohingya at
OL,14,Fsea, often ignoring reports of boats
OL,15,Fin distress.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
