OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,F"Stronger regional and international
OL,7,Fefforts are needed to prevent further
OL,8,Floss of life along one of the world's
OL,9,Fdeadliest maritime routes, including
OL,10,Fthrough enhanced search and rescue
OL,11,Fefforts, access to asylum and
OL,12,Fprotection, and actions against
OL,13,Fsmuggling and trafficking networks,"
OL,14,Fthe agencies said.
