OL,3,CMore than 500 feared dead amid reports
OL,4,Cof Rohingya refugee boats capsizing
OL,6,FMore than 6,500 Rohingya fled and
OL,7,Fnearly 900 were reported dead or
OL,8,Fmissing in 2025, the deadliest year
OL,9,Ffor Rohingya who tried to leave by
OL,10,Fboat. The figure represents the
OL,11,Fhighest mortality rate of any major
OL,12,Froute for refugee and migrant sea
OL,13,Fjourneys in the world, the UNHCR said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
